snippet.title: Missing Emma Sweet 2 - Tina McQuaig Cold Case - Sophia Felicita Moreno - Melissa Trumpy
snippet.description:
#truecrime #coldcase  #emmasweet #tinaMcQuaig #sophiafelicitamoreno #MelissaTrumpy
"earchers are continuing to look for a 2-year-old girl near the White River south of Columbus. Emma Sweet was last seen Wednesday, Nov. 24 in Bartholomew County.

Sheriff's deputies responded to the 1700 block of Blessing Road on the west side of the river around 6 a.m. Friday for a truck that was in the river. Duck hunters found the truck, which had one person in it, later identified as Jeremy Sweet. " -https://www.wthr.com/
